insert into public.article_translations (article_id, language_code, slug, title, excerpt, body, seo_title, seo_description) values ('53360a7d-80a7-520b-8586-9f67995debbf', 'en', 'vancouver-fan-festival-express-bus-plan', 'Vancouver points fans to an express bus for the Hastings Park Fan Festival', 'Vancouver 2026 says the Fan Festival Express bus will link SkyTrain stations with Hastings Park during peak World Cup viewing periods.', 'Vancouver''s official Fan Festival guidance is now detailed enough for practical route planning. The host committee says the free-to-enter Hastings Park festival will be served by the 11 Fan Festival Express bus from 29th Avenue SkyTrain Station and Renfrew Station, running every five minutes during peak hours, with limited parking and early arrival recommended.

The key instruction is simple: use SkyTrain, then transfer to the dedicated express bus. Vancouver 2026 says service will run from 29th Avenue on the Expo Line and Renfrew on the Millennium Line to the PNE grounds at Hastings Park.

The guidance recommends arriving at least one hour before match broadcasts and live performances for free viewing areas. Fans with amphitheatre tickets are advised to arrive 30 to 60 minutes before kickoff. Those windows matter because security screening, capacity and transfer queues can all stack up.

Vancouver''s match stadium and Fan Festival are not the same trip. BC Place sits near downtown SkyTrain access, while the PNE site requires a separate Hastings Park plan. Fans trying to do both in one day should treat the transfer as a real itinerary leg.

CupMate users should save the PNE as the Fan Festival destination, add the preferred SkyTrain station, and keep a backup arrival route for Canada matches or major concerts. The practical win is avoiding a last-minute search for parking near Hastings Park.', 'Vancouver points fans to an express bus for the Hastings Park Fan Festival', 'Vancouver 2026 says the Fan Festival Express bus will link SkyTrain stations with Hastings Park during peak World Cup viewing periods.') on conflict (article_id, language_code) do update set slug = excluded.slug, title = excluded.title, excerpt = excluded.excerpt, body = excluded.body, seo_title = excluded.seo_title, seo_description = excluded.seo_description;
insert into public.article_translations (article_id, language_code, slug, title, excerpt, body, seo_title, seo_description) values ('53360a7d-80a7-520b-8586-9f67995debbf', 'ru', 'vancouver-fan-festival-express-bus-hastings-park', 'Vancouver направляет болельщиков на express bus к Fan Festival', 'Vancouver 2026 описывает маршрут Fan Festival Express от SkyTrain к Hastings Park во время пиковых периодов.', 'Официальная инструкция Vancouver 2026 уже достаточно конкретна для планирования маршрута. Fan Festival на Hastings Park/PNE будет обслуживать автобус 11 Fan Festival Express от станций 29th Avenue SkyTrain и Renfrew, а в пиковые часы он должен ходить каждые пять минут.

Главный вывод для болельщиков: не искать несуществующую станцию Hastings Park SkyTrain и не рассчитывать на парковку. Лучше строить маршрут через SkyTrain и express bus, закладывая минимум час до трансляций и концертов на бесплатных площадках.

