insert into public.article_translations (article_id, language_code, slug, title, excerpt, body, seo_title, seo_description) values ('7f384630-76b9-5f4e-b04c-3e219038f083', 'en', 'iran-world-cup-squad-group-g-travel', 'Iran''s World Cup squad update sharpens travel plans for Group G supporters', 'Amir Ghalenoei has named a 30-player preliminary Iran squad, with Mehdi Taremi included and Sardar Azmoun absent before two Los Angeles matches.', 'IR Iran''s Group G picture is more concrete after FIFA reported that Amir Ghalenoei named a 30-player preliminary squad. Mehdi Taremi is included, while Sardar Azmoun is a notable omission, and the team is set for two Los Angeles matches before a Seattle finale.

The preliminary squad leans on experience but leaves out one of Iran''s best-known forwards. FIFA reported that Taremi is in the extended group while Azmoun, Allahyar Sayyadmanesh and Mohammad Javad Hosseinnejad were not included.

Iran begin Group G with two matches at Los Angeles Stadium: New Zealand on June 15 and Belgium on June 21. That gives traveling supporters a chance to use one hotel base for the first week, but it also concentrates demand around the same stadium, transport routes and fan gathering areas.

The group closer against Egypt moves the campaign north. Fans trying to attend all three Iran matches should separate the Los Angeles hotel block from the Seattle leg rather than treating it as a single city stay.

CupMate users should save Los Angeles Stadium twice, add a Seattle transfer reminder and keep the final squad deadline visible. Player omissions can change demand for specific fan events, especially when a team has a large diaspora following in U.S. host cities.', 'Iran''s World Cup squad update sharpens travel plans for Group G supporters', 'Amir Ghalenoei has named a 30-player preliminary Iran squad, with Mehdi Taremi included and Sardar Azmoun absent before two Los Angeles matches.') on conflict (article_id, language_code) do update set slug = excluded.slug, title = excluded.title, excerpt = excluded.excerpt, body = excluded.body, seo_title = excluded.seo_title, seo_description = excluded.seo_description;
insert into public.article_translations (article_id, language_code, slug, title, excerpt, body, seo_title, seo_description) values ('7f384630-76b9-5f4e-b04c-3e219038f083', 'ru', 'iran-sostav-chm-marshrut-gruppy-g-los-angeles', 'Состав Ирана уточняет маршрут болельщиков по группе G', 'Амир Галенои назвал предварительный список Ирана из 30 игроков: Мехди Тареми включен, Сардар Азмун отсутствует.', 'Картина группы G для Ирана стала конкретнее: FIFA сообщила, что Амир Галенои назвал предварительный состав из 30 игроков. Мехди Тареми включен, а Сардар Азмун стал главным отсутствующим именем.

Для болельщиков важна не только спортивная часть, но и маршрут. Иран проведет первые два матча в Los Angeles Stadium — против New Zealand 15 июня и Belgium 21 июня. Это позволяет планировать Лос-Анджелес как основную базу первой недели, но также повышает нагрузку на один стадионный район, транспорт и точки встреч.

