CupMate users following Korea Republic should save Guadalajara as the base for the opening week, add a Monterrey transfer reminder and keep official squad updates pinned until final registration is confirmed.', 'Korea Republic squad news sets up a practical Group C route for fans', 'Hong Myungbo has named Korea Republic''s 26-player World Cup squad, led by Son Heungmin, Kim Minjae and other experienced names.') on conflict (article_id, language_code) do update set slug = excluded.slug, title = excluded.title, excerpt = excluded.excerpt, body = excluded.body, seo_title = excluded.seo_title, seo_description = excluded.seo_description;
insert into public.article_translations (article_id, language_code, slug, title, excerpt, body, seo_title, seo_description) values ('b00ef7e4-bf64-5365-8f1e-44614c646e19', 'ru', 'koreya-sostav-chm-marshrut-gruppy-c-meksika', 'Состав Korea Republic задает практический маршрут по группе C', 'Хон Мён Бо назвал заявку из 26 игроков во главе с Son Heungmin, Kim Minjae и другими опытными лидерами.', 'Состав Korea Republic на Чемпионат мира стал публичным. FIFA сообщила, что Хон Мён Бо выбрал 26 игроков, включая Son Heungmin, Kim Minjae, Hwang Heechan, Lee Kangin и других знакомых лидеров.

